Trump Attacks Clinton on Energy Stance

In his first major address on energy policy, in Bismarck, N.D., presumptive GOP presidential nominee Donald Trump attacked Hillary Clinton over her position on fossil fuels and vowed to boost energy-related jobs in the U.S. Photo: AP
